Package project3

Class Parttime

java.lang.Object
project3.Employee
project3.Parttime
public class Parttime
extends Employee
Parttime class is an extension of the Employee class. It is for part time employees and holds an employees pay rate, hours worked.
Author:
Shane Hoffman, Michael Li
